- [ ] Logo redirects to Homepage
- [ ] No broken links are present
- [ ] Page layout is not broken

## 2. Cards Section
- [ ] Cards section opens correctly
- [ ] Debit Cards page is accessible
- [ ] Credit Cards page is accessible
- [ ] Card information is displayed correctly
- [ ] Text content is readable
- [ ] Buttons and links work correctly

## 3. Credits Section
- [ ] Credits section opens correctly
- [ ] Loan information is displayed
- [ ] No empty or broken blocks on the page
- [ ] Navigation back to homepage works

## 4. Deposits Section
- [ ] Deposits page opens successfully
- [ ] Deposit information is visible
- [ ] Page content matches menu selection

## 5. Online Banking
- [ ] Online Banking page opens
- [ ] Login button is visible
