## 6. Contacts & Branches
- [ ] Contacts page opens
- [ ] Contact information is displayed
- [ ] Branch information is visible
- [ ] Phone numbers and addresses are readable

## 7. Content Verification
- [ ] Text content is correct and readable
- [ ] No spelling or grammatical errors
- [ ] Currency symbols are displayed correctly
- [ ] Language consistency across pages

## 8. Responsiveness
- [ ] Website displays correctly on desktop
- [ ] Layout does not break on smaller screens
- [ ] Text remains readable on all resolutions

## 9. Browser Compatibility
- [ ] Website works correctly in Google Chrome
- [ ] Website works correctly in Mozilla Firefox

## 10. Production Smoke Checks
- [ ] Website is accessible on production
- [ ] Main pages open without errors
- [ ] Navigation works correctly
